lead_paragraph: Bud Norris pitched two perfect innings and Nick Markakis homered in the Atlanta Braves' 9-6 spring loss to the Pittsburgh Pirates on Saturday.

headline.print_headline: Norris Pitches Well in Atlanta's Loss to Pittsburgh
